    Hell Beast looked to Manterror, and as he began to speak, two large arms 
grabbed him and pulled him into darkness. Nighteyes was there two, she 
slipped inside in the confusion.  Shuffleing around he realized he had been 
pulled into the ship. With a quick flick of his wrist he slide a daggar out 
of his wrist and dug it deep into whoever was holding him.
    "AH, Starscream, alas Im sorry to have stabbed you but I have my own 
agenda to execute. Good bye!" He said, and fired two optic b;lasts at the 
bot, then running down the corridor insearch of what he needed.
    Nighteyes looked at Starscream and then fired a missle after Hell Beast. 
"Starscream, are you ok? Dont worry, he wont last long in here!"

    Megatron, now a safe distance from the autoguns thought the message over. 
And he agreed. A council was just the thing to end the MAximal reign of 
goodness. Predacon athorioty needed to be exercised.
    "Kitkat, Megatron here, I accept your offer....but, do return Hell Beast. 
I would hate to have to destroy your ship to get him back."

    Aracnia, Rampage, Tankkor, and Paralysis made there way to the ship. 
Aracnia looked around, "Kitkat, were here."
